## Write a program to convert rupees to paise

```
Input  ( Rs ) : 1
Output ( Ps ) : 100
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-rupees-to-paise" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    double rupees, paise;
    printf("Enter price in rupees: ");
    scanf("%lf", &rupees);  

    paise = rupees * 100;

    printf("%.2lf rupees = %.2lf paise", rupees,paise);

    return 0;
}
```

